        <div type="level2">
         <head>On the use of these materials</head>
         <p>You migth not be the kind of person that sits and read the guidelines page by page trying out new things. Or you might simply prefer another format or presentation.
         For these reason, and to allow for a shared base of shared presentations, some of which originally based on the training materials
         of <ref target="https://wiki.digitalclassicist.org/EpiDoc_Workshops">EpiDoc</ref>,  we share here the training materials we have used, divided in programms and single presentations.
         The programms of each workshop will use a different selection of the presentations and at different moment in the life of the project. Those presentations as they were given at that point
       will be linked in the programms, or only with the participants of that specific training, while the latest shareable version of a given presentation is linked below. </p>
</div>
